{"type":"message","id":"8da1d3e6","parentId":"aba7edaa","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:34:03.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to check the GitHub Actions build status for the jetton-monitor repository. Let me first read the GitHub automation skill to understand the best approach, then check the build status.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_OPlanwQL1KBN5SBAYNEZfjlN","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/skills/github-automation/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":59,"output":70,"cacheRead":23552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773642840755}}
{"type":"message","id":"83678265","parentId":"8da1d3e6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:34:03.874Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_OPlanwQL1KBN5SBAYNEZfjlN","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: github-automation\ndescription: GitHub 自动化操作与 CI/CD 管理。使用 GitHub CLI (gh) 和 REST/GraphQL API 进行仓库管理、Release 发布、PR 审查、工作流监控等自动化任务。当用户需要执行以下操作时使用：(1) 创建 GitHub Release 版本发布，(2) 检查 PR 状态或合并代码，(3) 监控 CI/CD 工作流运行状态，(4) 批量管理 Issue 或标签，(5) 查询仓库统计信息，(6) 自动化 Git 工作流\n---\n\n# GitHub 自动化\n\n## 概述\n\n使用 GitHub CLI (gh) 和 API 进行仓库管理、Release 发布、PR 审查、CI/CD 监控等自动化操作。\n\n## 核心能力\n\n### 📦 Release 自动化\n\n- 自动生成版本发布 (`gh release create`)\n- 自动生成 CHANGELOG\n- 附件自动上传 (zip、二进制文件)\n- 预发布版本标记\n\n```bash\n# 创建新版本发布\ngh release create v1.0.0 --title \"Version 1.0.0\" --notes \"Release notes\"\n\n# 生成带附件的发布\ngh release create v1.0.0 dist/*.zip --generate-notes\n\n# 查看最近发布\ngh release list --limit 10\n```\n\n### 🔍 PR 智能审查\n\n- CI 状态检查 (`gh pr checks`)\n- 代码冲突检测\n- PR 信息完整性校验\n- 自动合并策略 (squash/rebase)\n\n```bash\n# 检查 PR 的 CI 状态\ngh pr checks 55 --repo owner/repo\n\n# 列出最近的 PR\ngh pr list --state open --limit 20\n\n# 查看 PR 详情\ngh pr view 55 --json number,title,state,mergeStateStatus\n\n# 合并 PR\ngh pr merge 55 --squash\n```\n\n### ⚡ CI/CD 监控\n\n- 工作流运行状态查询 (`gh run list`)\n- 失败日志自动提取 (`gh run view --log-failed`)\n- 批量重试失败任务\n- 构建时间趋势分析\n\n```bash\n# 列出最近的工作流运行\ngh run list --repo owner/repo --limit 10\n\n# 查看特定运行的详情\ngh run view 123456789 --repo owner/repo\n\n# 只查看失败步骤的日志\ngh run view 123456789 --repo owner/repo --log-failed\n\n# 重试失败的运行\ngh run rerun 123456789 --repo owner/repo\n```\n\n### 📊 Issue 管理\n\n- 批量标签管理\n- 重复 Issue 检测\n- 自动回复模板\n- 里程碑跟踪\n\n```bash\n# 列出 Open 的 Issue\ngh issue list --state open\n\n# 创建 Issue\ngh issue create --title \"Bug: ...\" --body \"描述\"\n\n# 添加标签\ngh issue edit 123 --add-label \"bug,high-priority\"\n```\n\n## 高级 API 查询\n\n使用 `gh api` 进行自定义查询：\n\n```bash\n# 获取 PR 的特定字段\ngh api repos/owner/repo/pulls/55 \\\n  --jq '.title, .state, .user.login, .mergeable'\n\n# 列出最近的提交\ngh api repos/owner/repo/commits \\\n  --jq '.[] | \"\\(.sha[:7]): \\(.commit.message)\"' | head -10\n\n# 获取仓库统计信息\ngh api repos/owner/repo \\\n  --jq '.stargazers_count, .forks_count, .open_issues_count'\n\n# GraphQL 查询\ngh api graphql -f query='\n  query {\n    viewer {\n      login\n      repositories(first: 5) {\n        nodes {\n          name\n          stargazerCount\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n'\n```\n\n## 自动化工作流示例\n\n```\n[ 代码提交 ] → [ CI 运行 ] → [ 自动检查 ]\n      ↓\n[ PR 创建 ] → [ 审查 + CI 检查 ]\n      ↓\n[ 合并到 main ] → [ 自动打标签 ] → [ 生成 Release ]\n      ↓\n[ 通知飞书群组 ]\n```\n\n## 常用场景命令速查\n\n| 场景 | 命令 |\n|------|------|\n| 查看仓库状态 | `gh repo view --json url,defaultBranchRef` |\n| Fork 仓库 | `gh repo fork owner/repo` |\n| 克隆仓库 | `gh repo clone owner/repo` |\n| 创建分支 | `git checkout -b feature/xxx` |\n| 推送分支 | `git push -u origin feature/xxx` |\n| 创建 PR | `gh pr create --title \"xxx\" --body \"xxx\"` |\n| 查看 CI 状态 | `gh pr checks` |\n| 合并 PR | `gh pr merge` |\n| 创建 Release | `gh release create v1.0.0 --generate-notes` |\n| 查看工作流 | `gh run list` |\n\n## 认证配置\n\n```bash\n# 登录 GitHub CLI\ngh auth login\n\n# 使用 Token 认证（CI/CD 环境）\ngh auth login --with-token < token.txt\n\n# 查看当前认证状态\ngh auth status\n```\n\n## 参考资料\n\n- [GitHub CLI 官方手册](https://cli.github.com/manual/)\n- [GitHub REST API 文档](https://docs.github.com/en/rest)\n- [GitHub GraphQL API](https://docs.github.com/en/graphql)\n- [GitHub Actions 文档](https://docs.github.com/en/actions)\n- [jq 文档](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/) - JSON 处理工具\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642843874}}
